item.title: CVE-2017-6141|2024-09-16T22:09:37.413Z -- f5%20networks%2C%20inc. -- f5%20big-ip%20ltm%2C%20aam%2C%20afm%2C%20apm%2C%20asm%2C%20link%20controller%2C%20pem%2C%20websafe
item.description: In F5 BIG-IP LTM, AAM, AFM, APM, ASM, Link Controller, PEM, and WebSafe 12.1.0 through 12.1.2, certain values in a TLS abbreviated handshake when using a client SSL profile with the Session Ticket option enabled may cause disruption of service to the Traffic Management Microkernel (TMM). The Session Ticket option is disabled by default.
